56:37.743 --> 56:39.342
Oh, my God! Oh!

56:39.344 --> 56:41.311
This whole thing
is so fucked, dude.

56:41.313 --> 56:42.412
I know.

56:42.414 --> 56:44.648
What are we doing?

56:44.650 --> 56:47.050
You don't believe
this shit, do you?

56:47.052 --> 56:48.785
Fuck no!

56:48.787 --> 56:53.123
But I mean...
It's weird shit going on.

56:53.125 --> 56:54.724
Why, you don't believe it, do you?

56:54.726 --> 56:58.294
No. No. It's a mind fuck though.

56:58.296 --> 57:02.432
I mean, the noises last night?
And the drawing?

57:02.434 --> 57:03.933
Freaky shit, right?

57:03.935 --> 57:07.303
Yeah. But no,
Frankenstein is fiction.

57:07.305 --> 57:10.407
And Jonathan, for a genius,
is a fucking idiot.

57:10.409 --> 57:12.042
Amen to that.

57:20.084 --> 57:22.018
They're gonna be fine, right?

57:22.020 --> 57:25.088
I think so.

57:25.090 --> 57:27.357
Yeah.

57:27.359 --> 57:28.992
I wouldn't be worried about them.

57:28.994 --> 57:33.029
Really, it's broad daylight.

57:33.031 --> 57:36.833
I'm pretty sure the creature has
developed a nocturnal way of life.

57:36.835 --> 57:38.835
He shies away from people.

57:38.837 --> 57:41.805
He's generally moving at
night, sleeps during the day.

57:41.807 --> 57:43.840
They're fine.

57:43.842 --> 57:47.811
Aren't you concerned at all
if he were to come here?

57:47.813 --> 57:51.448
No. Of course not. How could I be?

57:51.450 --> 57:53.717
That's been my goal
the entire time.

57:53.719 --> 57:56.286
I've been clear about
that, haven't I?

57:56.288 --> 58:00.257
I want this. I need this proof.

58:00.759 --> 58:03.860
I'm getting kicked out
of the university.

58:03.862 --> 58:05.128
Anne told me.

58:05.130 --> 58:06.996
She did?

58:08.232 --> 58:10.967
Then you understand
how much I need it.

58:10.969 --> 58:14.871
Everything I've been working
on hinges on meeting him.

58:14.873 --> 58:19.776
That's the whole point of this, is
to have real photographic evidence.

58:19.778 --> 58:24.414
It's the only way I'm ever gonna prove to
my colleagues, to the world that I'm right.

58:24.516 --> 58:26.752
And I know I am.

58:28.754 --> 58:30.954
No doubt in my mind that I'm right.

58:59.083 --> 59:01.951
Fuck me!

59:01.953 --> 59:03.319
I don't want to go in there.

59:03.321 --> 59:05.088
You think I do?

59:05.090 --> 59:10.360
